istryGrid-shareGodsLove.jpg" alt="Resources to Build Your Faith" class="img-fluid d-block mx-auto rounded mb-2" loading="lazy"><h6>Resources to Build Your Faith</h6><p class="cta-button-group d-flex flex-wrap gap-2 my-3 justify-content-start"><a href="/faith" target="_blank" class="btn btn-secondary gap-1 mt-2">Learn More</a></p></div></div></div></div>
